<i>(FLASHBACK JOSIE'S VOICE) alright
then, you've gotta promise.</i>

01:00:59.056 --> 01:01:01.390
<i>You gotta promise, okay?
That this is your last trip, alright?</i>

01:01:01.392 --> 01:01:03.191
<i>(FLASHBACK) SHOOTER: yes.
JOSIE: please?</i>

01:01:03.193 --> 01:01:06.128
<i>(FLASHBACK) SHOOTER: I
promise... I promise.</i>

01:01:06.130 --> 01:01:07.696
<i>♪ ♪</i>

01:01:07.698 --> 01:01:09.398
TOMMY: and then what?

01:01:09.400 --> 01:01:11.266
Do you think it's
time for bed, huh?

01:01:11.268 --> 01:01:12.934
Come on,
just a bit more.

01:01:12.936 --> 01:01:16.872
<i>(SIGHS)</i>
well...

01:01:16.874 --> 01:01:19.841
alright, let me see.

