<i>♪ ♪</i>

01:02:00.884 --> 01:02:02.317
<i>♪ ♪</i>

01:02:02.319 --> 01:02:05.120
<i>now in that area,
there was a cave system</i>

01:02:05.122 --> 01:02:09.224
<i>that many said ran some
5 miles underground.</i>

01:02:09.226 --> 01:02:11.493
<i>TOMMY: 5 mile cave!</i>

01:02:11.495 --> 01:02:13.795
<i>SAM: you got it.</i>

01:02:13.797 --> 01:02:15.931
<i>Shooter knew that if he could
stash the loot,</i>

