<i>(GOLD CLANKING ON GROUND)</i>

01:02:28.245 --> 01:02:30.245
<i>(STRIKING MATCH)</i>

01:02:33.250 --> 01:02:36.885
<i>(GRUNTING)</i>

01:02:36.887 --> 01:02:40.989
<i>(DIGGING SOUNDS)</i>

01:02:40.991 --> 01:02:44.359
<i>♪ (TENSE MUSIC) ♪</i>

01:02:44.361 --> 01:02:46.762
<i>(DIGGING SOUNDS)</i>

01:02:46.764 --> 01:02:51.466
<i>♪ (TENSE MUSIC) ♪</i>

01:02:51.468 --> 01:02:53.535
<i>meanwhile, doc had
reached tucson and told</i>

01:02:53.537 --> 01:02:56.772
<i>earp his version of
what had happened.</i>

01:02:56.774 --> 01:02:58.206
<i>Just like shooter figured,</i>

01:02:58.208 --> 01:03:00.876
<i>doc pinned the whole
thing on him.</i>

