EARP: I need men I can trust;
I trusted this man,

01:03:04.448 --> 01:03:07.382
and he betrayed us.

01:03:07.384 --> 01:03:09.117
He took the wealth of
this good city,

01:03:09.119 --> 01:03:15.991
